Package: dure
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10)
Description: resource-aware community LLM node bootstrapper
 Dure inventories Linux nodes, joins them to a trusted controller, plans model
 placement, provisions Ray/vLLM containers, and verifies readiness. The central
 server is installed separately with the Python server extra.
